sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant Panel as TotpCodePanel
    participant Api as ApiClient
    participant Server as Express
    participant TotpH as totpHelper
    participant DB as SQLite

    Note over User,DB: 密钥Tab激活
    Panel->>Api: GET /api/totp/codes
    Api->>Server: request with JWT
    Server->>DB: SELECT * FROM totp_entries WHERE user_id=?
    DB-->>Server: entries array
    Server->>TotpH: decryptSecret + generateTOTP for each
    TotpH-->>Server: [{id, label, code, remaining, period}]
    Server-->>Api: codes array
    Api-->>Panel: codes data

    Panel->>Panel: renderCodes() — SVG环形进度条 + 6位码
    Panel->>Panel: startAutoRefresh() — setInterval(500ms)

    loop 每500ms检查倒计时
        Panel->>Panel: updateProgressRings() — SVG stroke-dashoffset动画
        Panel->>Panel: 当 remaining <= 0 → fetchCodes() 重新获取
    end

    User->>Panel: 点击某码的"复制"按钮
    Panel->>Panel: navigator.clipboard.writeText(code)
    Panel->>User: Toast提示"已复制"
